</P>
<P>
   ``The filing was, in fact, precipitated by our bank syndicate
having declared a technical default under a trade finance
agreement. This entire situation has caught us by surprise,''
Solomon said. ``We are a leader in our industry and are confident
that we have the support of our key technical partners and our key
customers, as required, to hopefully emerge from this in an
expeditious manner.''
</P>
<P>
   Last week, just prior to Thursday's filing, the company was
forced to suspend its business.
</P>
<P>
   Its building, equipment and inventory were seized by a group of
