paper and prepares to make another pile with a new career _ writer.
Turns out she ain't half bad. O, The Oprah Magazine hits newsstands
nationwide Wednesday morning, trumpeting on its cover an
irresistible promise: ``Live Your Best Life!'' Does it deliver?
Maybe _ if you're a woman 25-49 in search of ``a personal-growth
guide,'' as Winfrey describes her mag. (Neal, Palm Beach Post). 22.
