<P>
   (Coded ``s'')
</P>
<P>
   RAC-VECSEY-COLUMN (Undated) _ Leah Gyamati, a female trainer
with a Masters in Theology, was hired by 40 entry-level investors
in part because of their interest in involving a woman. She has
turned into a rousing success at Aqueduct. By George Vecsey.
</P>
<P>
   BKN-RHODEN-COLUMN (Boston) _ Column on the New York Knicks, who
after basically standing around all season waiting for the playoffs
to begin, will now begin the playoffs this weekend against a team
that has given them trouble _ Toronto. By William C. Rhoden.
</P>
<P>
   BKN-KNICKS-CELTICS (Boston) _ Knicks at Boston, 7 p.m. Knicks
finish out the regular season against the Celtics. By Selena
Roberts.
