7:30 p.m. Another sad season draws to a close for the Nets.
</P>
<P>
   BKN-PLAYOFF-SCHEDULE (New York) _ There appears to be some
intrigue surrounding the first-round playoff schedule for the NBA
and in the middle of it all are the Knicks and Vince Carter.
</P>
<P>
   BBA-YANKS-RANGERS (Arlington, Texas) _ New York at Texas, 3:05
p.m. By Buster Olney.
</P>
<P>
