Jack Curry.
</P>
<P>
   BOX-GATTI-WEIGHT (New York) _ Arturo Gatti appears at a luncheon
trumpeting his place on the undercard of the Lewis-Grant fight, so
reporters can watch how much he eats and observe how he appears to
be able to gain and lose weight so quickly. By Bill Pennington.
</P>
<P>
   UTENN-ATHLETES (Knoxville, Tenn.) _ A review of the academic
records of 39 Tennessee football and basketball players by a
tenured member of the faculty who is a longtime critic of the
athletic department, finds a pattern of questionable practices,
including many juniors and seniors who never declare a major, lots
of altered grades, and a bunching of many athletes in the urban
studies department, all taking the same courses. By Teri Bostian.
</P>
