<HEADER>
A1504 &Cx1f; taf-z
u v AM-PAGE1-CONSIDER-NYT     04-19 0549
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE>
 
</HEADLINE>
 AM-PAGE1-CONSIDER-NYT
<TEXT>
<P>
   Here are the stories New York Times editors are considering for
the Page 1 of Thursday, April 20. The N.Y. Times News Service night
supervisor is Ned Kilkelly; phone: (888) 346-9867.
</P>
<P>
   INTERNATIONAL
</P>
