</P>
<P>
   MILK-JUGS (Los Angeles) _ Hoping to juice up its sales, the
dairy industry is making the first changes in 50 years to the
plastic jug. Pitcher-style containers are showing up in stores
along with snazzy single-serving bottles of flavored milk. By Chris
Sieroty.
