<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-04-19 23:49 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2050 &Cx1f; ttd-z
r f BC-HP-PRINTER-SFCHRON &LR;      04-19 0553
